---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="relative pt-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-20 -left-20 w-72 h-72 bg-blue-400/20 rounded-full blur-3xl dark:bg-blue-600/10"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-20 -right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-orange-400/20 rounded-full blur-3xl dark:bg-orange-600/10"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 mb-10 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            User Guide
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-titles font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            Learn how to use
            <span class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-orange-500 dark:from-blue-400 dark:to-accent">
                Dialcash
            </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-body text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
            Organize your expenses and income in a simple and conscious way
        </p>
        <div class="bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-linear-to-br from-blue-500 to-orange-500 dark:from-blue-600 dark:to-accent flex items-center justify-center">
                    <Icon name="tabler-lightbulb" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-titles font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                    Introduction
                </h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lg font-body text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                Dialcash is designed to help you understand your money clearly. 
                It doesn't seek to replace a bank or automate everything, but rather give you 
                <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">control and visibility</span> 
                over your personal finances.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <a 
                href="#workflow"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 hover:bg-blue-100 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/30 rounded-full transition-colors"
            >
                <Icon name="tabler-rocket" class="w-4 h-4" />
                <span>Dialcash Workflow</span>
            </a>
            <a 
                href="#features"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-orange-600 dark:text-accent bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 hover:bg-orange-100 dark:hover:bg-orange-900/30 rounded-full transition-colors"
            >
                <Icon name="tabler-star" class="w-4 h-4" />
                <span>Features</span>
            </a>
            <a 
                href="#tips"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 rounded-full transition-colors"
            >
                <Icon name="tabler-lightbulb" class="w-4 h-4" />
                <span>Tips & Tricks</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>